name: Kiwi Fruit Farming Packet
description: The Kiwi Fruit Farming Packet is unlocked in theWorkshopon theSpace Stationand is equipped in the Prospectors loadout before starting a new prospect. Only after landing on Icarus can the packet be consumed, giving the Prospector five Kiwifruit seeds, which then can be planted inDirt MoundsorCrop Plotsto growKiwifruit.
